subject: NCAA Basketball Championships (Men)
Basketball (College)
lead_paragraph: Tim Henderson, a walk-on at Louisville, and Spike Albrecht, a 5-foot-11 guard at Michigan, have made important contributions to their teams heading into the national title game.
